{"tid":317913,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（放榜攻略）睇到呢個Post嘅DSE雞，祝你地入到8大！","createTime":"2017-07-11T18:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T11:02:22.000Z","uid":57076,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a90aef29f77ef77b34c6ce94012ed24bf528cb94","tid":317913,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:33:07.000Z","msg":"今年有21339人考到3322最低入大學資格，其實只要有17-18分都已經夠入大學，但排Jupas真係要好小心，而以下幾點有時係必須注意<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.該科收幾多個jupas學生</span><br />\n記住每科都有個quota，而BBA/sciences/social sciences/engine等等科目普遍都有大類收生，人數比較多，詳情每間大學都唔同，最緊要收人數夠多，如果你分數過lower quartile都可以博A1<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 每間大學學生總數</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個重點好容易比人忽視，而每間大學學生人數如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/021903_11d3d9ec1d316f871319b46c287f3e80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F021903_11d3d9ec1d316f871319b46c287f3e80.jpg&h=53ae5fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每間大學學生總數，各科人數詳情可以到以下網址搜索<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdcf.ugc.edu.hk/cdcf/searchUniv.do?lang=TC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdcf.ugc.edu.hk%2Fcdcf%2FsearchUniv.do%3Flang%3DTC&d=Hjxnf1Uv6oAoTQJOP%2F3ZeZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d49a58cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdcf.ugc.edu.hk/cdcf/searchUniv.do?lang=TC</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 以上數字未必有計算自資學位<br />\n<br />\n以上2點點咁重要？ 因為當某間大學某科收生數目比較多，而個收生分數通常range都大，可以博得過（除左神科）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.過往收生DSE成績參考</span><br />\n我以前就參考以下呢個網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.atu.hk/results/2016/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.atu.hk%2Fresults%2F2016%2F&d=Hjxnf1Uv6oAoTQJOP%2F3ZeZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ef3cdeec\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.atu.hk/results/2016/</a><br />\n但<br />\n<br />\nA1 A2 A3 <br />\nA1可以博lower Quartile個分<br />\nA2-A3 最好就起碼有mean/median個分<br />\n<br />\n最後就係，入到大學就恭喜你，而就算入唔到大學，天無絕人之路，如果想讀上去就試下Asso/hd/retake，唔想讀書就早D學專業，出黎打工<br />\n<br />\n讀緊大學乞食科既經驗話比我知，大學其實係一個比你延遲踏入社會既一個水泡，你遲早都要入呢個社會，早日學識游出公海都未嘗唔係一件好事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後一點係，唔好以為公開試係人生一切，唔好因為公開試放棄自己，呢個雖然係一個人生交叉點，但絕對唔係終點，前面條路仲好漫長！</span></span>"},{"pid":"38eb8fd9af543a92d3d8b23c5e94d1640b8b7f05","tid":317913,"uid":57076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:36:34.000Z","msg":"留意ATUHK上面以往成績有真有假 有成績單先好參考"},{"pid":"520f720acde90552faa67e0a372724089515e2db","tid":317913,"uid":97330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"上左岸都大大力比個支持你<br />\n幫下啲師弟師妹手！"},{"pid":"b93a3828cdaab239a737e22c44364755ce551ed7","tid":317913,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上左岸都大大力比個支持你<br />\n幫下啲師弟師妹手！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n突然有感而發姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f22037af9630835636b997a888febfb56986e3","tid":317913,"uid":54256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:51:36.000Z","msg":"如果你對社會時事議題，政府政策，政府運作有興趣既<br />\n可以考慮下報CCCU Public Administration and Management (PAM)<br />\n呢科會有好多政策，時事既野；<br />\nyear1 暑假仲會有政黨 intern比你做 (計學分，姐係要比錢)<br />\n亦都會有FYP；FYP係會包括政策辯論，政策分析，訪問仲會整條片出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有咩問題可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 今年畢業有UGC offer"},{"pid":"72223ae0c9fc8483439cd54744920476acc12b84","tid":317913,"uid":54256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cb3c552db68b112301fb59b11921b7c2733a5c","tid":317913,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你對社會時事議題，政府政策，政府運作有興趣既<br />\n可以考慮下報CCCU Public Administration and Management (PAM)<br />\n呢科會有好多政策，時事既野；<br />\nyear1 暑假仲會有政黨 intern比你做 (計學分，姐係要比錢)<br />\n亦都會有FYP；FYP係會包括政策辯論，政策分析，訪問仲會整條片出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有咩問題可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 今年畢業有UGC offer</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCCCU 唔係要賣盤啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"383fd2c9395edd292a15b0f4ffd1274155de45dc","tid":317913,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:08:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1bf54acd0ed421db44311cb9ba3ad3360531d2d6","tid":317913,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:16:37.000Z","msg":"今年考生少左，收聲分數普遍應該下降，應該可以搏低過lower quartile少少既科"},{"pid":"c248d4c0de7f9961e6441fa5b4b18e5b4720861c","tid":317913,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年考生少左，收聲分數普遍應該下降，應該可以搏低過lower quartile少少既科</blockquote><br />\n其實都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0153b3d7b312049e8b9fdc6e44884647baac16","tid":317913,"uid":96367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有個唔開cccu既問題想問，求巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCusus social worker有冇伏？想聽日去walkin<br />\n我個情況都幾特殊，我一早已報左cusus社工但冇去到interview <br />\n咁佢已sd email叫我13-15號可以去翻面試，但我又驚，想聽日12號再去報名即場面試，唔知咁得唔得？"},{"pid":"3ca6b577b98a386fdd5e8d79e12e771901f679d3","tid":317913,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有個唔開cccu既問題想問，求巴打解答<img